<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="weak-adj">weak <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /wi:k/    美 /wi:k/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-strong-tough">1.★ <strong>虚弱的 反【strong / tough】；微弱的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The child was weak from hunger and almost fell.
这孩子饿得虚弱无力，差点摔倒。</p><footer>外研⑦ – 3</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a weak ray of light
一道微弱的光线</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>不擅长的；(能力等) 差的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>weak points</strong>
弱点</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He is <strong>weak in</strong> mathematics, but good at English.
他数学差，但英语好。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ ****</h4>
<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>weakly /'wiːkli/ adv   </p></div>